outputs.output_descr: The Project will assist the Ministry of Forestry to strengthen its coordination capacity on international cooperation, to strengthen monitoring of ongoing initiatives, and to identify gaps in addressing forestry and climate change in Indonesia and prepare new initiatives accordingly. This Project Initiation Plan is funded by the UNDP Country Office and will work closely with other relevant initiatives such as the UN-REDD Joint Programme.

project_descr: Forest and Climate Change (CC): To strengthen the Government of Indonesia's capacity to address forest and climate change issue.
